    "name": "The RPG Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3221750,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RPG-Lite</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想象一下任何幻想类 RPG，但简化并彻底颠覆传统元素。  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需吃东西即可治愈伤口 - 只需将一片面包塞入伤口即可。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需整理要卖给商人的东西：收集的所有东西都被视为“战利品”，你可以按重量出售一堆战利品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >库存和升级，但没有复杂的技能树和库存管理。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >龙，主要反派，不断出现故障并违反游戏规则。找出原因！好吧... 或者不找。这是你的选择，而且非常重要，就像 RPG 中的选择一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有钓鱼迷你游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/a387ee1284364bdb69006d45c69816d7.poster.avif?t=1754536322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/a387ee1284364bdb69006d45c69816d7.webm?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/a387ee1284364bdb69006d45c69816d7.mp4?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地下城如同扭曲的迪士尼乐园</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在岛屿管理部门负责的地下城中，有一个技术楼层，里面的工作人员要确保火把点亮、陷阱正常运作，以及突袭后的怪物得到治愈。最底层隐藏着一个可以让你有机会彻底颠覆故事情节的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/5cc14ea2d7dffed0c36ae4c857590b88.poster.avif?t=1754536322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/5cc14ea2d7dffed0c36ae4c857590b88.webm?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/5cc14ea2d7dffed0c36ae4c857590b88.mp4?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细规划你的目标、动作和弹药。准备好大汗淋漓吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/fd51f545f5a7816b05e035b43da80f59.poster.avif?t=1754536322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/fd51f545f5a7816b05e035b43da80f59.webm?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/fd51f545f5a7816b05e035b43da80f59.mp4?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >储备火把。有很多地方值得探索！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/370949a5bfab5814fd82693d6b449f53.poster.avif?t=1754536322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/370949a5bfab5814fd82693d6b449f53.webm?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/370949a5bfab5814fd82693d6b449f53.mp4?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>坚韧的秘密</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被困在冒险岛上。岛上有一个景点——地下城，你可以在那里突袭、探索、抢劫、获得经验并升级。只需购买冒险者门票，通过旋转栅门，进入电梯并选择楼层即可。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理部门确保陷阱正常工作、火把点亮并且怪物在突袭后得到治愈。乍一看，对于有抱负的冒险家来说，一切都似乎很完美，那为什么要离开呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/6ba0afde07830c2bb1218d3099657d24.poster.avif?t=1754536322\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/6ba0afde07830c2bb1218d3099657d24.webm?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3221750/extras/6ba0afde07830c2bb1218d3099657d24.mp4?t=1754536322\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事实证明，一切并非表面看起来的那样。酷王隐藏着一个黑暗肮脏的秘密。怪物们厌倦了不断的重生循环，他们的生活就像土拨鼠一样。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但主怪物毛刺龙失控了，打破了游戏规则，以便为他的（非）天才计划找到合适的人选。或许是你？由你来决定！</p>",
